data.description: Don’t miss this welcoming, move-in ready, well maintained full brick home, with 4-bedrooms 3.5-baths, and a huge OFFICE in Madison! Perfectly laid out OPEN floor plan, has beautiful hardwoods throughout main living areas. The inviting kitchen has granite countertops, high-top seating, island and stainless-steel appliances. The primary suite is spacious and situated on its own wing with en-suite. While bedrooms 2 & 3 share jack-and-jill style bath, bedroom 4 can be the perfect in-law/guest room with its own full-bath. Newly installed ceiling fans in all rooms, and a huge laundry. The side entry garage is followed by an extended driveway, that includes a cement walkway to a covered back porch.
